long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Murano Dev Helper is a browser plugin on manifest V3 designed to simplify the development process of Murano's team. 

It is used to automatically add related task links and special logic to dev websites and environments (Teamcity, GitHub, Crucible, Sentry, Wrike, NUnit playlists).
